<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>trnymạt rwḥyẗ</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ại̹lahī ạản̊ta sanadī .. tawakũlī ʿalaẙk̊
 ạảyãạmu ʿum̊rī kulũhā .. yā rabũ fī yadaẙk̊

[V2]
 2- min̊ ṭāridīã najĩnī .. kadẖāka min̊ ạảʿ̊dāẙ
 ạảḍī̊̉ biwaj̊hika ạl̊bahī̃̊ .. ʿalayã yā maẘlạaẙ

[V3]
 3- ại̹lahunā rabũ ạlsãmā .. ại̹lahunā ạl̊muʿīn̊
 fī sit̊rihi ạảs̊kananī .. fī maʿ̊qiliⁿ ḥaṣīn̊

[V4]
 4- mā ạảʿ̊ẓama ạl̊jūda ạlãdẖī .. dẖakẖar̊tahu lil̊bār̃̊
 tas̊turuhu bisit̊rika .. min̊ ḥīali ạlạảsẖ̊rār̊

[V5]
 5- yā ạảt̊qīāʾu ạảḥ̊bibūạ .. ại̹lahanā ạl̊wadūd̊
 fāi̹nãhu ạlrãbũ ạl̊ʿalī̃̊ .. waḥāfiẓu ạl̊ʿuhūd̊

[V6]
 6- wal̊yatasẖajãʿ̊ qal̊bukum̊ .. yā kẖāyỉfī ạlại̹lah̊
 mun̊taẓirīna raḥ̊maẗaⁿ .. lil̊maj̊di wāl̊ḥayāh̊</lyrics>
<title>ạlhy ạnt sndy</title>
</song>